text: Yerenis Yisel De León Batista (born 23 February 1995) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a defender for Ecuadorian club Carneras UPS FC and the Panama women's national team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
title: Yerenis De León
